column5: Fishello everybody Does anybody have any info if the ice on west shore, Gillford - Innisfil, is still good to walk? Was thinking about trying to get one more jumbo dinner before the meltdown. Appreciated! Thanks!
hmmmeah...I guess I should have asked if anybody's willing to PM me info anonymously so there's no lawsuit after I drown under the ice
My friend told me that he is still ice fishing out of Innisfil.  He usually just walks out.
Ice was still good in Innisfil on Saturday, shoreline was ok too.   Things could change quickly with the current forecast though.
